  "detailed_description": "<strong>Welcome to Neko Loop.</strong><br>Neko Loop is a roguelike game with resource management and constant progression where your decisions have great influence on the course of each game.<br>Unlock secrets, defeat bosses, meet characters and do your best to help Selina get back home.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBAT</h2></strong><br>Face a variety of enemies in intense battles:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/f47fb8e1b93c7dc46eefd857f25dd48d.poster.avif?t=1761410154\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/f47fb8e1b93c7dc46eefd857f25dd48d.webm?t=1761410154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/f47fb8e1b93c7dc46eefd857f25dd48d.mp4?t=1761410154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EQUIPMENT SYSTEM</h2></strong><br>Equip powerful items and become stronger.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/f1d2a02beea8eb21202d862005dc9a3d.avif?t=1761410154\" width=580 height=512 /></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CARDS AND RESOURCES:</h2></strong><br>Unlock cards with various effects, get resources and use them to your advantage<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/e88aa4c871cf8cbadb52fa108e41a5e6.poster.avif?t=1761410154\" width=580 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/e88aa4c871cf8cbadb52fa108e41a5e6.webm?t=1761410154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/e88aa4c871cf8cbadb52fa108e41a5e6.mp4?t=1761410154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/0f98731f0b85635717c0350bf7c9f775.poster.avif?t=1761410154\" width=580 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/0f98731f0b85635717c0350bf7c9f775.webm?t=1761410154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055470/extras/0f98731f0b85635717c0350bf7c9f775.mp4?t=1761410154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>And much more!",
